<title>
Identification Plate
</title>
<ptxt>
Identification plate (1) is installed at the center pillar lower side on the right or left side body panel.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
The identification plate has the following information:
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
VIN (2)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Vehicle type (3)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Engine type (4)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Color code (5)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Model code (6) including the model information shown in 
<intxref refid = "AENBP70A0101010001">Model Code Description</intxref>
 below.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70B010003.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "124.662mm" ver = "01" gw = "185" gh = "337"/>
